  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Apple News Format makes it easy to create side-by-side content, such as a caption that floats next to the article body. On sufficiently wide displays, News automatically lays out such a caption in the article margin; on narrower displays, News automatically stacks the caption with other article content.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "media-3624920",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "On this page, you’ll learn how to create a caption that appears in the right margin of the article on wide displays.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "strong"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Create-a-ComponentLayout-Object-for-the-Floating-Caption",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Create a ComponentLayout Object for the Floating Caption",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Before you can position the caption in the right margin, you must define a component layout object that specifies that the caption will begin in column 7 of the article layout and span three columns.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Copy the example code ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNews/creating-a-floating-caption#sideCaptionLayout-Copy-This-Code",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Paste the code between the closing brace (",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "}",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ") of the last ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "ComponentLayout",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " object and the closing brace for the whole ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "componentLayouts",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " property.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Your code should look like the example code ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNews/creating-a-floating-caption#sideCaptionLayout-Result",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "sideCaptionLayout-Copy-This-Code",
          "level": 4,
          "text": "sideCaptionLayout: Copy This Code",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            ",",
            "    \"sideCaptionLayout\": {",
            "      \"columnStart\": 14,",
            "      \"columnSpan\": 6,",
            "      \"margin\": {",
            "        \"bottom\": 24",
            "      }",
            "    }"
          ],
          "syntax": "json",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "sideCaptionLayout-Result",
          "level": 4,
          "text": "sideCaptionLayout: Result",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "{",
            "  ...",
            "  \"componentLayouts\": {",
            "    ...",
            "    \"sideCaptionLayout\": {",
            "      \"columnStart\": 14,",
            "      \"columnSpan\": 6,",
            "      \"margin\": {",
            "        \"bottom\": 24",
            "      }",
            "    }",
            "  },",
            "  ...",
            "}"
          ],
          "syntax": "json",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Anchor-the-Caption-to-the-Article-Body",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Anchor the Caption to the Article Body",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "On wide displays, when you anchor a caption to the article body, the caption’s top edge will be aligned with the body’s top edge; on narrower displays, the caption will be stacked above the body.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Delete the ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "caption",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " component and its parent container from your header. \u2028The code you’re deleting begins with the comma and opening brace (,",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "{",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ") before ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "\"role\": \"container\",",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " and ends with a mix of three alternating braces and brackets, and a comma (",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "}]}",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ").",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Copy the example code ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNews/creating-a-floating-caption#Caption-Copy-This-Code",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Paste the code inside your article’s second section, before the opening brace (",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "{",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ") of the ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "body",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " component whose text begins with ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "Nam libero tempore",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "text": "Inside the ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "body",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " component whose text begins with ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "Nam libero tempore",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", add an ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "identifier",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " property with a value of ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "\"body1\"",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ", as shown in the example code ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.applenews/documentation/AppleNews/creating-a-floating-caption#Caption-Result",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "After you make these changes in your ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "article.json",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " file, you can preview your working ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "article.json",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " file in News Preview to see the floating caption.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Caption-Copy-This-Code",
          "level": 4,
          "text": "Caption: Copy This Code",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "        {",
            "          \"role\": \"container\",",
            "          \"layout\": \"sideCaptionLayout\",",
            "          \"anchor\": {",
            "            \"targetComponentIdentifier\": \"body1\",",
            "            \"targetAnchorPosition\": \"top\",",
            "            \"originAnchorPosition\": \"top\"",
            "          },",
            "          \"components\": [",
            "            {",
            "              \"role\": \"caption\",",
            "              \"format\": \"html\",",
            "              \"layout\": \"fullBleedLayout\",",
            "              \"text\": \"ABOVE: Sed ut pers piciatis unde omnis iste error sit volup tatem accusa ntium dolor emque, totam rem. (Attribution)\"",
            "            }",
            "          ]",
            "        },"
          ],
          "syntax": "json",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Caption-Result",
          "level": 4,
          "text": "Caption: Result",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Ellipses (",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "...",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ") indicate lines of code that have been omitted from this example.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "{",
            "  ...",
            "  \"components\": [",
            "    ...",
            "    {",
            "      \"role\": \"section\",",
            "      ...",
            "      \"components\": [",
            "        ...",
            "        {",
            "          \"role\": \"container\",",
            "          \"layout\": \"sideCaptionLayout\",",
            "          \"anchor\": {",
            "            \"targetComponentIdentifier\": \"body1\",",
            "            \"targetAnchorPosition\": \"top\",",
            "            \"originAnchorPosition\": \"top\"",
            "          },",
            "          \"components\": [",
            "            {",
            "              \"role\": \"caption\",",
            "              \"format\": \"html\",",
            "              \"layout\": \"fullBleedLayout\",",
            "              \"text\": \"ABOVE: Sed ut pers piciatis unde omnis iste error sit volup tatem accusa ntium dolor emque, totam rem. (Attribution)\"",
            "            }",
            "          ]",
            "        },",
            "        {",
            "          \"identifier\": \"body1\",",
            "          \"role\": \"body\",",
            "          \"format\": \"html\",",
            "          \"layout\": \"noMarginLayout\",",
            "          \"textStyle\": \"bodyFirstDropCap\",",
            "          \"text\": \"<p>Nam libero tempore, cum soluta nobis est eligendi optio cumque nihil impedit quo minus id quod maxime placeat facere possimus, omnis voluptas assumenda est, dolor repellendus. <a href='http://www.apple.com'>Link text</a> quibusdam et aut.</p><p>Nemo enim ipsam voluptatem quia voluptas sit aspernatur aut odit aut fugit, sed quia consequuntur magni dolores eos qui ratione voluptatem sequi nesciunt. Neque porro quisquam est, qui dolorem ipsum quia dolor sit amet, adipisci velit.</p>\"",
            "        },",
            "        ...",
            "      ]",
            "    }",
            "  ],",
            "  ...",
            "}"
          ],
          "syntax": "json",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
